en=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 10, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104wky1665703007912.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wky1665703007912.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wky1665703007912.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"wky1665703007912\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $formmodality\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"wky1665703007912___formmodality_267143\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return an indication of the form modality for the requested form instance.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"wky1665703007912__topic_d83993e1_d83994e1_d83995e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wky1665703007912__p_d83996e1_d83997e1_d83998e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$formmodality</span> { <code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">InstanceName</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code> }</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wky1665703007912__topic_d55577e1_d55578e1_d55579e1_d55580e1_d55581e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d807916e75\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"wky1665703007912__table_d8693e1_d8694e1_d8695e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"wky1665703007912__table_d8693e1_d8694e1_d8695e1__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"wky1665703007912__table_d8693e1_d8694e1_d8695e1__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"wky1665703007912__table_d8693e1_d8694e1_d8695e1__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wky1665703007912__table_d8693e1_d8694e1_d8695e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">InstanceName</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wky1665703007912__table_d8693e1_d8694e1_d8695e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wky1665703007912__table_d8693e1_d8694e1_d8695e1__entry__3\">\n Component instance name; optional. If omitted, the modality of the current form instance is returned.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wky1665703007912__topic_d55582e1_d55583e1_d55584e1_d55585e1_d55586e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d807916e129\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"wky1665703007912__table_d8696e1_d8697e1_d8698e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$formmodality</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"wky1665703007912__table_d8696e1_d8697e1_d8698e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Value \n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"wky1665703007912__table_d8696e1_d8697e1_d8698e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wky1665703007912__table_d8696e1_d8697e1_d8698e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n 1\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wky1665703007912__table_d8696e1_d8697e1_d8698e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n                        InstName is a modal form.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wky1665703007912__table_d8696e1_d8697e1_d8698e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n 0\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wky1665703007912__table_d8696e1_d8697e1_d8698e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n                        InstName is a non-modal form.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wky1665703007912__table_d8696e1_d8697e1_d8698e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n \"\"\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wky1665703007912__table_d8696e1_d8697e1_d8698e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n An error occurred.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wky1665703007912__p_d84005e1_d84006e1_d84007e1\">If an error occurs, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> contains a negative value that identifies the exact error.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"wky1665703007912__table_d8699e1_d8700e1_d8701e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 3. </span><span class=\"title\">Values of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> Commonly Returned Following\n                  <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$formmodality</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"wky1665703007912__table_d8699e1_d8700e1_d8701e1__entry__1\">\n Value \n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"wky1665703007912__table_d8699e1_d8700e1_d8701e1__entry__2\">\n Error constant\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"wky1665703007912__table_d8699e1_d8700e1_d8701e1__entry__3\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wky1665703007912__table_d8699e1_d8700e1_d8701e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-57</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wky1665703007912__table_d8699e1_d8700e1_d8701e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UACTERR_NO_INSTANCE&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wky1665703007912__table_d8699e1_d8700e1_d8701e1__entry__3\">\n The named instance cannot be found in the component pool.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wky1665703007912__table_d8699e1_d8700e1_d8701e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-1105</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wky1665703007912__table_d8699e1_d8700e1_d8701e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_INSTANCE&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wky1665703007912__table_d8699e1_d8700e1_d8701e1__entry__3\">\n The instance name provided is not valid (For more information, see the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">newinstance</span> ProcScript statement); for example, the argument contains incorrect characters.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wky1665703007912__table_d8699e1_d8700e1_d8701e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-1304</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wky1665703007912__table_d8699e1_d8700e1_d8701e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_UNKNOWN_CONTEXT&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"wky1665703007912__table_d8699e1_d8700e1_d8701e1__entry__3\">\n Function not allowed, unknown context. For example, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$formmodality</span> was used without the InstName argument and no instance is current.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wky1665703007912__topic_d55587e1_d55588e1_d55589e1_d55590e1_d55591e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d807916e316\">\n                       \n Use\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"wky1665703007912__p_d84011e1_d84012e1_d84013e1\">Use in Form components.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wky1665703007912__section_urd_wyz_zbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d807916e326\">Example: Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$formmodality</span></h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following example puts a message in the message frame that\n               indicates if the current instance was started as a modal or non-modal form:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"wky1665703007912__pre_by2_yyz_zbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">if ($formmodality = 1)\n putmess \"%%$instancename is modal.\"\nelse\n putmess \"%%$instancename is non-modal\"\nendif\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fxx1665702529732.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>activate</a><p>Calls an operation on a component instance.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ryt1665702577808.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>newinstance</a><p>Creates a new instance of a component.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533394\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533394\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$formmodality Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $formmodality Return an indication of the form modality for the requested form instance. $formmodality { ( InstanceName ) } Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description InstanceName String Component instance name; optional. If omitted, the modality of the current form instance is returned. Return Values Table 2. Values returned by $formmodality Value Meaning 1 InstName is a modal form. 0 InstName is a non-modal form. \"\" An error occurred. If an error occurs, $procerror contains a negative value that identifies the exact error. Table 3. Values of $procerror Commonly Returned Following $formmodality Value Error constant Meaning -57 <UACTERR_NO_INSTANCE> The named instance cannot be found in the component pool. -1105 <UPROCERR_INSTANCE> The instance name provided is not valid (For more information, see the newinstance ProcScript statement); for example, the argument contains incorrect characters. -1304 <UPROCERR_UNKNOWN_CONTEXT> Function not allowed, unknown context. For example, $formmodality was used without the InstName argument and no instance is current. Use Use in Form components. Example: Using $formmodality The following example puts a message in the message frame that indicates if the current instance was started as a modal or non-modal form: if ($formmodality = 1) putmess \"%%$instancename is modal.\" else putmess \"%%$instancename is non-modal\" endif Copy Related Links activate Calls an operation on a component instance. newinstance Creates a new instance of a component. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}